#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:870(para) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2112(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:870(para)
msgid ""
"Copy the <filename>/etc/squid/squid.conf</filename> file and protect it from "
"writing with the following commands entered at a terminal prompt:"
msgstr ""

#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:875(command) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2117(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:875(command)
