#: ../generic/server/C/network-config.xml:442(para) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:913(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/network-config.xml:442(para)
msgid ""
"This method entails defining a pool (sometimes also called a range or scope) "
"of IP addresses from which DHCP clients are supplied their configuration "
