#: ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:202(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:202(para)
msgid ""
"The <application>libsasl2-2</application>, <application>sasl2-"
"bin</application> and <application>libsasl2-modules</application> are "
